msgid ""
"Restore, resubmit, and rescale Klein for Ray jobs from durable checkpoints."
msgstr "从持久检查点恢复、重新提交并扩缩 Klein for Ray 作业。"

msgid "Restore and rescale a job"
msgstr "恢复作业并调整并行度"

msgid "This guide covers two recovery paths:"
msgstr "本指南介绍两条恢复路径："

msgid "an in-place worker or coordinator restart inside the same live job; and"
msgstr "在同一个活动作业内原地重启 worker 或协调器；以及"

msgid ""
"a new submission after the JobManager, Ray head node, or entire cluster was "
"lost."
msgstr "JobManager、Ray head 节点或整个集群丢失后重新提交。"

msgid ""
"In-place recovery automatically uses the current job's latest completed "
"checkpoint. A new submission needs the explicit URI of one completed `chk-N` "
"directory in `execution.savepoint.path`."
msgstr "原地恢复会自动使用当前作业最新完成的检查点。新的提交需要在 `execution.savepoint.path` 中显式指定一个已完成的 `chk-N` 目录 URI。"

msgid ""
"This guide uses *rescale* for changing concurrency while rebuilding a graph "
"from a checkpoint. To change one operator inside a running job, use the "
"barrier-aligned procedure in [Autoscaling and live operator rescaling]"
"(operator-rescaling.md)."
msgstr "本指南中的“调整并行度”是指从检查点重建图时更改并发度。若要更改运行中作业的单个算子，请使用[自动扩缩与在线算子扩缩容](operator-rescaling.md)中的屏障对齐流程。"

msgid "Prepare before failure"
msgstr "故障前准备"

msgid ""
"Use shared durable storage and retain more than one checkpoint while "
"operating an important job:"
msgstr "运维重要作业时，请使用共享持久存储，并保留多个检查点："

msgid "Keep the following with the deployment definition:"
msgstr "请将以下内容与部署定义一并保存："

msgid "source topics, consumer identities, and start-position policy;"
msgstr "数据源 topic、消费者身份和起始位置策略；"

msgid "the graph-building code and stable operator names;"
msgstr "图构建代码和稳定的算子名称；"

msgid "`state.keyed.max-parallelism`;"
msgstr "`state.keyed.max-parallelism`；"

msgid "serializer, schema, and connector versions;"
msgstr "序列化器、模式和连接器版本；"

msgid "checkpoint storage URI and credential mechanism;"
msgstr "检查点存储 URI 和凭据机制；"

msgid "output idempotency or deduplication key."
msgstr "输出幂等性或去重键。"

msgid ""
"Node-local RocksDB and Ray Object Store snapshots accelerate live recovery "
"but cannot recover a lost cluster."
msgstr "节点本地 RocksDB 和 Ray Object Store 快照可加速在线恢复，但无法恢复已丢失的集群。"

msgid "Select a completed checkpoint"
msgstr "选择已完成的检查点"

msgid "A restorable directory contains `_metadata`:"
msgstr "可恢复目录包含 `_metadata`："

msgid ""
"Prefer the newest `chk-N` whose `_metadata` is readable. `_latest` is only "
"an optimization; Klein falls back to scanning completed checkpoint "
"directories when the pointer is missing, stale, or corrupt. Do not select an "
"incomplete directory that lacks `_metadata`."
msgstr "优先选择 `_metadata` 可读的最新 `chk-N`。`_latest` 只是一项优化；指针缺失、过期或损坏时，Klein 会回退为扫描已完成的检查点目录。不要选择缺少 `_metadata` 的不完整目录。"

msgid ""
"Job snapshots and checkpoint logs expose recent completion and failure "
"history. They do not copy durable checkpoint payloads into the state actor."
msgstr "作业快照和检查点日志会公开近期完成及失败历史，但不会将持久检查点载荷复制到状态 actor。"

msgid "Resubmit from the checkpoint"
msgstr "从检查点重新提交"

msgid ""
"Recreate the same logical graph and pass the complete checkpoint-directory "
"URI:"
msgstr "重新创建相同的逻辑图，并传入完整的检查点目录 URI："

msgid ""
"The restore path is intentionally singular: it names one completed "
"checkpoint, not the checkpoint root. Configuration accepts unknown keys for "
"application metadata, so a misspelling such as `execution.checkpointing."
"restore-path` is a silent no-op. Use the canonical `execution.savepoint."
"path` key."
msgstr "恢复路径有意设计为单个路径：它指定一个已完成检查点，而不是检查点根目录。配置会接受未知键作为应用元数据，因此 `execution.checkpointing.restore-path` 这类拼写错误会静默无效。请使用规范的 `execution.savepoint.path` 键。"

msgid ""
"When resubmitting on the same cluster, stop the old job first. A stable `job."
"namespace` is useful for operational attachment, but reusing a namespace "
"while its old detached actors still exist can address the wrong job. After a "
"whole-cluster loss the old actors no longer exist."
msgstr "在同一集群上重新提交时，请先停止旧作业。稳定的 `job.namespace` 便于运维连接，但若旧的分离 actor 仍存在，复用命名空间可能会连接到错误作业。整个集群丢失后，旧 actor 已不存在。"

msgid "Change parallelism during restore"
msgstr "恢复期间更改并行度"

msgid ""
"Managed keyed state is partitioned into a fixed key-group space. You may "
"change the concurrency of keyed operators during restore when all of these "
"remain true:"
msgstr "托管键控状态划分在固定的键组空间中。恢复时可以更改键控算子的并发度，但必须同时满足以下条件："

msgid ""
"`state.keyed.max-parallelism` is unchanged and is not below the new "
"concurrency."
msgstr "`state.keyed.max-parallelism` 保持不变，且不小于新的并发度。"

msgid ""
"The same logical operators, stable names, state descriptors, and serializers "
"are reconstructed."
msgstr "重建相同的逻辑算子、稳定名称、状态描述符和序列化器。"

msgid ""
"Source and sink connectors support the new parallelism. For example, Kafka "
"source concurrency above the useful partition count adds idle subtasks."
msgstr "Source 和 Sink 连接器支持新的并行度。例如，Kafka Source 并发度超过有效分区数只会增加空闲子任务。"

msgid ""
"External systems tolerate any changed connection or transaction fan-out."
msgstr "外部系统能够承受连接数或事务扇出的变化。"

msgid ""
"Klein assigns each restored subtask a contiguous key-group range and loads "
"only the fragments it now owns. Keys are not rehashed with Python's process-"
"local `hash()`."
msgstr "Klein 为每个恢复的子任务分配连续键组范围，并且只加载它现在拥有的分片。键不会通过 Python 的进程本地 `hash()` 重新哈希。"

msgid ""
"Never change max parallelism for a job whose checkpoint must remain "
"restorable. Treat state descriptor names and serialized value shapes as "
"schema."
msgstr "如果作业的检查点必须保持可恢复，则绝不能更改最大并行度。请把状态描述符名称和序列化值结构视为模式。"

msgid "Validate the restored job"
msgstr "验证恢复后的作业"

msgid "Before returning traffic or trusting output, check:"
msgstr "恢复流量或信任输出前，请检查："

msgid "the job reaches `RUNNING` rather than repeatedly entering recovery;"
msgstr "作业进入 `RUNNING`，而不是反复进入恢复；"

msgid "the first completed checkpoint after restore succeeds;"
msgstr "恢复后的第一个检查点成功完成；"

msgid ""
"`state_durable_restore_fallbacks` and restore-duration metrics match the "
"expected recovery path;"
msgstr "`state_durable_restore_fallbacks` 和恢复耗时指标符合预期恢复路径；"

msgid ""
"Kafka lag or another source-position metric resumes near the checkpoint;"
msgstr "Kafka 延迟或其他数据源位置指标在检查点附近恢复；"

msgid "no unexpected late-record or sink-commit failures appear;"
msgstr "没有出现意外的迟到记录或 Sink 提交失败；"

msgid "output deduplication absorbs the accepted replay window."
msgstr "输出去重能够覆盖可接受的重放窗口。"

msgid ""
"Use `ray-klein status <namespace>` for a summary and `ray-klein attach "
"<namespace>` for live progress."
msgstr "使用 `ray-klein status <namespace>` 查看概要，使用 `ray-klein attach <namespace>` 查看实时进度。"

msgid "Common restore failures"
msgstr "常见恢复故障"

msgid "Symptom"
msgstr "症状"

msgid "Likely cause"
msgstr "可能原因"

msgid "Action"
msgstr "操作"

msgid "`_metadata` missing"
msgstr "缺少 `_metadata`"

msgid "Incomplete checkpoint publication"
msgstr "检查点发布不完整"

msgid "Select an earlier completed `chk-N`."
msgstr "选择更早完成的 `chk-N`。"

msgid "Unsupported checkpoint format"
msgstr "不支持的检查点格式"

msgid "Code and checkpoint schema are incompatible"
msgstr "代码与检查点模式不兼容"

msgid ""
"Run the matching Klein version or a deliberate migration tool; do not edit "
"pickled metadata."
msgstr "运行匹配的 Klein 版本或有意设计的迁移工具；不要编辑 pickle 元数据。"

msgid "State checksum/size mismatch"
msgstr "状态校验和/大小不匹配"

msgid "Missing or corrupt state object"
msgstr "状态对象缺失或损坏"

msgid ""
"Verify object-store consistency and restore an earlier retained checkpoint."
msgstr "验证对象存储一致性，并恢复更早保留的检查点。"

msgid "Missing operator state"
msgstr "缺少算子状态"

msgid "Graph identity or operator construction order changed"
msgstr "图身份或算子构造顺序发生变化"

msgid "Rebuild the original logical graph and stable names."
msgstr "重建原始逻辑图和稳定名称。"

msgid "Max-parallelism mismatch"
msgstr "最大并行度不匹配"

msgid "`state.keyed.max-parallelism` changed"
msgstr "`state.keyed.max-parallelism` 已更改"

msgid "Restore with the original value."
msgstr "使用原值恢复。"

msgid "Connector cannot seek/restore"
msgstr "连接器无法定位/恢复"

msgid "Source recovery is broker-owned or custom state is incomplete"
msgstr "Source 恢复由 broker 管理，或自定义状态不完整"

msgid "Follow that connector's documented recovery boundary."
msgstr "遵循该连接器文档中的恢复边界。"

msgid "Output duplicates"
msgstr "输出重复"

msgid "Sink commit succeeded before the restored checkpoint became durable"
msgstr "Sink 在恢复的检查点持久化前已提交成功"

msgid "Apply the documented idempotency/deduplication design."
msgstr "应用文档中的幂等/去重设计。"

msgid ""
"Klein does not yet expose a user-triggered command that creates an "
"independently named savepoint. `execution.savepoint.path` restores from an "
"already completed checkpoint or compatible savepoint URI."
msgstr "Klein 尚未提供创建独立具名 savepoint 的用户触发命令。`execution.savepoint.path` 用于从已经完成的检查点或兼容 savepoint URI 恢复。"
